  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Project aims to determine the number of individuals with treatment resistant hypertension and
      to define the characteristics of these patients and estimate disease frequency. The study
      will be a retrospective review of medical record data based upon de‚Äêidentified information
      and will require no patient contact.
